life will only get harder for you.

1096
01:05:49,103 --> 01:05:50,909
I'm not Park Do Ra.

1097
01:05:50,933 --> 01:05:52,849
I'm Kim Ji Young.

1098
01:05:52,873 --> 01:05:55,104
